          <td class="code">
	        
            <div class="highlight"><pre><span class="gp">$</span> go run switch.go 
<span class="go">write 2 as two</span>
<span class="go">it&#39;s the weekend</span>
<span class="go">it&#39;s before noon</span>
</pre></div>

          </td>
        </tr>
        
